high_descs: Turn around and take one step, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Take the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and open the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and close the door for three seconds, then take the lettuce out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the lettuce on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn to your right and go to the open portion of the sink.
Pick up the lettuce that is in the sink.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator to your left.
Place the head of lettuce in the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the head of lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and go to the counter top to the left of the sink.
Place the head of lettuce on the counter, to the right of the pepper grinder.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold head of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the fridge, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the head of lettuce inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the head of lettuce then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.
